**üö® WARNING: GitHub MCP functions create git synchronization conflicts!**

**‚ùå NEVER USE these GitHub MCP functions for commits:**
- `push_files()` - Creates commits directly on GitHub, bypassing local git
- `create_or_update_file()` - Same synchronization issue
